snippet.title: Preston
snippet.description:
Hey y'all!

I’m a 25-year-old, Jesus loving, video game playing, vlogger from the great state of Texas! I live to make epic and exciting vlogs for all of you — my FireNation family!. 

If you’re a fan and wanna talk to me, just hit me up on Twitter! I love engaging with all of my fans! 🔥🔥🔥

Psalm 23:1: “The LORD is my shepherd, I lack nothing.”
